# Demo Applications Reference

## MaaS Demo (demo/maas-demo/)

Interactive Model as a Service demonstration.

### Entry Points
- `demo-maas.sh` - CLI demo launcher
- `maas-toolkit.sh` - Full MaaS toolkit
- `app.py` - Streamlit web interface
- `demo.sh` - Quick demo script
- `run-demo.sh` - Run demo with setup

### Library Files (lib/)
- `common.sh` - Common utilities
- `infrastructure.sh` - Infrastructure setup
- `model-catalog.sh` - Model catalog functions
- `model-discovery.sh` - Discover deployed models
- `tiers.sh` - Tier management (rate limiting)

### Scripts
- `deploy-app.sh` - Deploy demo application
- `setup-demo-model.sh` - Setup demo model
- `scripts/show-tier-metrics.sh` - Display tier metrics

### Manifests
- `manifests/deployment.yaml` - Demo deployment
- `manifests/authpolicy-with-tier-lookup.yaml` - AuthPolicy with tiers

### Features
- Chat with deployed models
- Compare model responses
- View MaaS metrics
- Tier-based rate limiting demo

